name: Carmen Electra
description:
Request, from all places, by my wife

Tara Leigh Patrick, known professionally as Carmen Electra, is an American actress, model, singer, and media personality. He has been a Pussycat Doll, a Las Vegas Headliner and posed for Playboy five times.

Trained on 1.5 base model, but examples are from Analog Madness and Consistent Factor

Skews NSFW(which is a little odd since none of the photos are from her playboy shoots), but SFW is doable

If you have any suggestions/comments/criticisms/or requests for the next model for me to make, please let drop me a comment.
